data.description: Welcome home to this exceptional property in the sought after Almaden Golf and Country Club neighborhood. Tucked on one of the most desirable streets overlooking the golf course at the 7th fairway. The sprawling single story home is beautifully updated with fresh interior paint, designer lighting, hardwood floors, new carpet, vaulted ceilings, skylights, dual pane windows, recessed lighting, 2 fireplaces and French doors to the rear yard. The stunning chef's kitchen features custom cabinetry, granite counters, gorgeous backsplash, stainless steel appliances and high-end Aga Legacy pro-style range oven. The spacious family room is an entertainer's delight with a wet bar and floor-to-ceiling windows for views of the pool and fairway. The primary suite is a true retreat with a sitting room and spacious bathroom. Enjoy the resort-like backyard with a sparkling pool, beautiful landscaping, multiple seating areas for entertaining and views of the golf course. The large 2 car garage features a bonus garage door facing the green for convenient golf cart access. Premier location just a few minutes walk to the Clubhouse. This one is a gem!!
